getModelAuthors

public java.util.List<Person> getModelAuthors()
Gets the value of the modelAuthors property.

This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the JAXB object. This is why there is not a set method for the modelAuthors property.

For example, to add a new item, do as follows: 

    getModelAuthors().add(newItem);
